title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Updates - World Update XI - released
description:
In this video we will look at the new additions to World Update XI: Canada which has been released today. What we know from the release notes is that it will add 87 Point of Interest which have been manually crafted. In addition to this the following cities received an update:

- Halifax
- Sherbrooke
- Abbotsford
- Saskatoon
-Toronto
- Montreal
- Regina
- Calgary
-Victoria
- St. Catharines
-Laval
- Vancouver
